      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·閔予小子之什·003.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">敬之.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>敬之敬之，天維顯思。
命不易哉！無曰高高在上。
陟降厥士，日監在茲。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Let me be reverent! Let me be reverent!
(The way of) Heaven is evident,
And its appointment ​is not easily preserved.
Let me not say that it is high aloft above me.
It ascends and descends about our doings;
It daily inspects us wherever we are.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
