      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·閔予小子之什·003.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">敬之.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>維予小子，不聦敬止？
日就月將，學有緝熙于光明。
佛時仔肩，示我顯德行。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I am a little child,
Without intelligence to be reverently (attentive to my duties);
But by daily progress and monthly advance,
I will learn to hold fast the gleams (of knowledge), till I arrive at bright intelligence.
Assist me to bear the burden (of my position),
And show me how to display a virtuous conduct.</seg>
      </tuv>
